Package com.navis.framework.persistence.quartz

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    ICustomDelegate
    This class provides an interface for delegate methods not provided by quartz.
    IJobGroupFilter
    This interface provides the method to be called for every trigger filter.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AbstractJobGroupFilter
    This class provides an abstract implementation for a series of ordered job filters.
    DefaultMSSqlDelegate
    This class...
    DefaultOracleDelegate
    This class is an override of the Oracle Quartz Delegate
    DefaultSQLDelegate
    This class is an extension of the StdJDBCDelegate that overrides the getObjectFromBlob method and does a check to make sure the binary input stream has data available.
    JobGroupFilterCPULoad
    This class filters out a trigger if current node is not the node with the lowest overall CPU load in the current job Group.
    JobGroupFilterManager
    This class serves as a utility to filter out job triggers based on pluggable criteria
    JobGroupFilterMinCPUs
    This class does a hard reject of the trigger if the minimum CPUs are not met
